Lesotho Bans Imports of Meat, Animal-Products From South Africa, Lena Says

-- B y   G o r d o n   B e l l
-- 
2011-03-04T09:58:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-04/lesotho-bans-imports-of-meat-animal-products-from-south-africa-lena-says.html
Lesotho banned imports of South
African meat and products from cloven-hoofed animals after a
suspected outbreak of foot and mouth disease in the neighboring
country, Lesotho News Agency reported, citing Ralechate Mokose,
the minister of agriculture.  The ban includes cattle, pigs, goats and sheep and their
products, and doesnâ€™t affect fish and chicken imports, the
Maseru-based agency cited Mokose as saying.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
